    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L V8, an atmospheric masterpiece delivering 414 hp through eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is paired with a tactile 6-speed manual and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior mechanical grip. Maintenance is current, with rod bearings and throttle actuators addressed to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis utilizes Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and aluminum multi-link suspension to provide precise feedback. Presented in honest 'good' condition, this car represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated M-performance, offering a visceral driving experience and a focused, driver-centric cockpit.",
