    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday reliability. The exterior retains its deep, high-gloss luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014honest signs of a car that has been enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium leather seats have been treated regularly to prevent cracking, showing only light bolstering wear on the driver's side. All onboard electronics, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, function exactly as they should. Mechanically, this car is in excellent health. It has followed a strict service schedule, with a recent oil change and a fresh set of performance tires installed just 2,000 miles ago. The engine pulls smoothly through the gears, and the suspension remains tight and responsive without any unusual rattles or squeaks. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been garage-kept and professionally detailed. It offers a turn-key experience for the next owner who values mechanical integrity and a clean, well-presented aesthetic.",
